c\">Mrs. April was an amazing educator. She was very much so relaxed but stern at the same. Being in a classroom for three hours is hard but she definitely made the time fly by. She is very caring and states driving laws directly. I would recommend her to any person no matter the age or background. She is Awesome!!</p></div></div><div class=\"advgb-testimonial-item\"><div class=\"advgb-testimonial-avatar-group\"><div class=\"advgb-testimonial-avatar\" style=\"background-image:url(http://localhost/amy/wp-content/plugins/advanced-gutenberg/assets/blocks/testimonial/avatar-placeholder.png);border-radius:50%;border-width:undefinedpx;width:120px;height:120px\"></div></div><div class=\"advgb-testimonial-info\"><h4 class=\"advgb-testimonial-name\">Janice</h4><p class=\"advgb-testimonial-position\" style=\"color:#fcb900\"></p><p class=\"advgb-testimonial-desc\">AWESOME DRIVING SCHOOL!!!! MRS. APRIL AND HER TEAM MADE THE EXPERIENCE EASIER FOR SOMEONE WHO IS A LIL OLDER TO FEEL JUST AS COMFORTABLE AS THE YOUNGER STUDENTS.</p></div></div></div><button class=\"advgb-slider-arrow advgb-slider-prev\" style=\"color:#fcb900;border-color:#fcb900;width:50px\"><svg fill=\"currentColor\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M15.41 16.59L10.83 12l4.58-4.59L14 6l-6 6 6 6 1.41-1.41z\"></path><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"></path></svg></button><button class=\"advgb-slider-arrow advgb-slider-next\" style=\"color:#fcb900;border-color:#fcb900;width:50px\"><svg fill=\"currentColor\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M8.59 16.59L13.17 12 8.59 7.41 10 6l6 6-6 6-1.41-1.41z\"></path><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"></path></svg></button></div>\n<!-- /wp:advgb/testimonial -->\n\n<!-- wp:social-links {\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"is-style-logos-only\"} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-social-links aligncenter is-style-logos-only\"><!-- wp:social-link 