131\",\"headerIcon\":\"plusCircleOutline\",\"headerIconColor\":\"#313131\",\"collapsedAll\":true,\"changed\":true,\"rootBlockId\":\"9b4a3c29-62ab-4bf6-960d-510c5c4b3c96\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-advgb-accordion-item advgb-accordion-item\" style=\"margin-bottom:15px\"><div class=\"advgb-accordion-header\" style=\"background-color:#fcb900;color:#313131;border-style:solid;border-radius:2px\"><span class=\"advgb-accordion-header-icon\"><svg fill=\"#313131\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0,0h24v24H0V0z\"></path><path d=\"M13,7h-2v4H7v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4V7z M12,2C6.48,2,2,6.48,2,12s4.48,10,10,10s10-4.48,10-10S17.52,2,12,2z M12,20 c-4.41,0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8,8-8s8,3.59,8,8S16.41,20,12,20z\"></path></svg></span><h4 class=\"advgb-accordion-header-title\" style=\"color:inherit\">DMV Certified Instructors&lt;br>to all ages and skill levels</h4></div><div class=\"advgb-accordion-body\" style=\"border-style:solid !important;border-color:undefined !important;border-top:none !important;border-radius:2px !important\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.newportdrivingschool.com/about-us.html\">With over 2 decades of Experience,</a>our driving school has the<a href=\"https://www.newportdrivingschool.com/reviews.html\">Best Driving School Reviews!!</a>and<a href=\"https://www.newportdrivingschool.com/images/binderperfectscore.pdf\">Best Driving School Results</a>! NDS have<a href=\"https://www.newportdrivingschool.com/dmv-certified-instructor.html\">DMV Certified Instructors</a>who offer lifelong driving skills to all ages and skill levels. Our Driving School is the choice all drivers has made for clear and simple reasons. We provide distinctive driving courses that are simplified and tailored to address the needs of every person willing to learn how to drive safely and efficiently and in the shortest timeframe.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:advgb/accordion-item --></div>